using Bluetooth.

00:02:34.050 --> 00:02:35.530
So let me highlight them.

00:02:35.530 --> 00:02:39.400
So the first one is in terms of power consumption.

00:02:39.400 --> 00:02:43.880
Bluetooth is really doing very well.

00:02:43.880 --> 00:02:46.580
Sometimes even better than wifi.

00:02:46.580 --> 00:02:57.160
