user experience there.

00:03:14.940 --> 00:03:26.319
And finally wifi direct is available in, I
believe, in ICS and so in terms of a compatibility,

00:03:26.319 --> 00:03:33.340
Bluetooth NFC is probably much more compatible
in all the Android devices.

