Jelly Bean and above your application should

00:04:58.160 --> 00:05:03.030
be already behaving much smoother than before.

00:05:03.030 --> 00:05:11.740
And having said that, there are several APIs
that you can take out, in order to take further

00:05:11.740 --> 00:05:15.740
advantage of this re-sync.

00:05:15.740 --> 00:05:25.900
