that you would like to do, whenever re-sync

00:05:25.900 --> 00:05:31.320
happens, probably you would like to simply
invalidate your field.

00:05:31.320 --> 00:05:37.650
Actually, that this Android animation framework
already has a method for that.

00:05:37.650 --> 00:05:44.610
And it is called view.postinvalidate on anime
shop.

00:05:44.610 --> 00:05:53.650
