the Android animation framework.

00:06:57.990 --> 00:07:08.039
Still, you can divinate this Jelly Bean project
Butter by using our new API called Choreographer.

00:07:08.039 --> 00:07:14.740
And this is a totally new API that we introduced
starting API developer 16.

00:07:14.740 --> 00:07:24.169
And you can basically say that the, this Choreographer
API is you can use when you would like to

00:07:24.169 --> 00:07:31.250
put your callback synchronized with this basic
timing.

00:07:31.250 --> 00:07:41.099
